{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"7":{"eng-name":"Fasting","ara-name":"كتاب الصيام"}},"section_detail":{"7":{"hadithnumber_first":1638,"hadithnumber_last":1782,"arabicnumber_first":1638,"arabicnumber_last":1782}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1733,"arabicnumber":1733,"text":"حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو بَكْرِ بْنُ أَبِي شَيْبَةَ، حَدَّثَنَا يَزِيدُ بْنُ هَارُونَ، عَنِ ابْنِ أَبِي ذِئْبٍ، عَنِ الزُّهْرِيِّ، عَنْ عُرْوَةَ، عَنْ عَائِشَةَ، قَالَتْ: كَانَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ـ صلى الله عليه وسلم ـ يَصُومُ عَاشُورَاءَ، وَيَأْمُرُ بِصِيَامِهِ ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih - Bukhari And Muslim"}],"reference":{"book":7,"hadith":96},"chapter":{"id":41,"ara-name":"باب صِيَامِ يَوْمِ عَاشُورَاءَ","eng-name":"Fasting the day of `Ashura’","isFirstHadith":true}}]}